file.name: testBasicObjectAndRef.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Corunet Challenge Game Server
  description: Test File for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
  contact:
    name: Corunet
    url: coru.net
    email: info@coru.net
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
- url: http://localhost:8080/v1
paths:
  /games:
    post:
      summary: Start a Game
      operationId: createGame
      description: Test File for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
      tags:
      - games
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Test File for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                  message:
                    $ref: "#/components/schemas/Message"
components:
  schemas:
    Message:
      type: object
      properties:
        description:
          type: string
tags:
- name: games
  description: Test description for SCC MultiApi Plugin.
